dcterms:creator: D.C. Van Essen
A.D. Edwards
N.D. Volkow
K. Marek
dcterms:description: The Human Connectome Project (HCP) dataset includes diffusion MRI data from young healthy adults, providing a comprehensive atlas of white matter tracts.
dcterms:title: Human Connectome Project (HCP)

dcterms:creator: A.D. Edwards
D.C. Van Essen
dcterms:description: The developing HCP (dHCP) dataset consists of diffusion MRI data from neonates, aimed at understanding brain development.
dcterms:title: developing HCP (dHCP)

dcterms:creator: N.D. Volkow
dcterms:description: The Adolescent Brain Cognitive Development (ABCD) dataset is a large-scale study focusing on brain development in adolescents, including various health and behavioral assessments.
dcterms:title: Adolescent Brain Cognitive Development (ABCD) dataset

dcterms:creator: K. Marek
dcterms:description: The Parkinson’s Progression Markers Initiative (PPMI) dataset provides data on Parkinson's disease patients and healthy individuals, focusing on the progression of the disease.
dcterms:title: Parkinson’s Progression Markers Initiative (PPMI) dataset

dcterms:description: The Brain Tumor Patient (BTP) dataset consists of diffusion MRI data from brain tumor patients, focusing on the unique challenges posed by tumor-related changes in brain structure.
dcterms:title: Brain Tumor Patient (BTP) dataset
